## 3. Project Documentation Based on Implemented Steps

### 3.1 Introduction

Subscription‚Äëbased platforms face challenges such as customer churn, low renewal rates, and inefficient manual renewal processes. This project introduces an AI‚Äëpowered chatbot to automate and optimize subscription renewals.

---

### 3.2 Objectives

* Predict renewal likelihood using ML
* Automate renewal communication
* Simplify membership benefits using ScaleDown
* Recover lapsed members
* Improve retention and revenue

---

### 3.3 Methodology

1. Data creation and exploration
2. Data preprocessing
3. Model training and evaluation
4. Renewal probability prediction
5. Offer personalization
6. Chatbot integration
7. Payment simulation
8. Result evaluation

---

### 3.4 System Design

The system integrates:

* Dataset and ML model
* Chatbot logic
* Offer engine
* Payment module

---

### 3.5 Results and Discussion

The system demonstrates how AI‚Äëdriven personalization and automation significantly improve renewal efficiency and user engagement.

---

### 3.6 Conclusion

The project successfully implements an end‚Äëto‚Äëend renewal management system using AI and machine learning. It reduces churn, automates communication, and improves business outcomes while remaining scalable and practical for real‚Äëworld deployment.

---

### 3.7 Future Enhancements

* Real payment gateway integration
* Deep learning‚Äëbased churn prediction
